abstract: Iraqi authorities say at least 50 people died in suicide car bombing in marketplace in eastern part of the country where people were shopping for Eid al-Fitr, holiday marking end of Ramadan.
lead_paragraph: At least 50 people were killed in a suicide car bombing in a central marketplace in eastern Iraq on Friday.

headline.main: Iraq: Dozens Killed in Car Bombing at End of Ramadan
headline.print_headline: Middle East; Iraq: Dozens Killed in Car Bombing at End of Ramadan
